# ============================================================================
# Excluded Pods
# ============================================================================
# List pod names that should be excluded from cleanup.
# These pods will not be deleted regardless of age.
#
# Format: One pod name per line
# Comments: Lines starting with # are ignored
# Whitespace: Leading/trailing whitespace is trimmed
#
# Note: This applies to standalone pods only. Pods managed by Deployments,
# ReplicaSets, Jobs, etc. are automatically excluded from cleanup.
#
# Examples:
#   long-running-job-pod
#   debug-pod
